{"tid":2386230,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財巴：WSB後時代，Chamath彈起繼續帶領SPAC股未來","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T23:32:20.000Z","uid":61161,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0609ebd54dd8572f34993151ccedc87b7d601de3","tid":2386230,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"長話短說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下影片有介紹Chamath背景<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aNY0sqSXmJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaNY0sqSXmJE&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=ce86cb45\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aNY0sqSXmJE</a><br />\n<br />\nChamath 經此一役聲明大噪<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wgYZk9Mc804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwgYZk9Mc804&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=c043dadc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wgYZk9Mc804</a><br />\n<br />\n以往由大戶主導嘅股票市場，將被散戶主導，美股將會A股化，源於散戶參與程度大大提高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n散戶參與程度提高有以下原因：<br />\n1. 打工過生活唔work，例如要做個識炒股嘅律師，用律師嘅人工去炒股<br />\n2. 智能電話普及，資訊愈來愈流通<br />\n3. 社交群體圍爐<br />\n以上原因集中於一大班不同國家嘅年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似你同我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NblnXaUGEdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNblnXaUGEdc&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=eb0ecda4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NblnXaUGEdc</a><br />\n<br />\n講埋有咩野關係同影響：<br />\n1. Chamath係Spac IPO系列嘅主要玩家之一<br />\n2. 散戶參與Spac嘅尋寶遊戲將會繼續，就好似呢度都有唔少巴絲一路埋伏同投資Spac股一樣<br />\n3. NAV價亦都成為咗不致於輸身家嘅保障<br />\n4. 由於流通量問題，基金較少於早期投資Spac股，除Arkk，最少都會等佢轉咗Code再發展一排先<br />\n<br />\n雖然財經台已經俾GME事件洗版，但我都唔會放棄繼續尋寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 睇下明唔明我想帶出啲乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明就讀多次個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n財巴：提防全民皆股，為泡沫爆破時做好準備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2381230\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2381230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"007a66e1e7ac1db813ed68efb9d6263f59f52d9e","tid":2386230,"uid":92841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"10207403d3e56976cdbc56839a759486a7d13c30","tid":2386230,"uid":300956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bd4a2f8d4adf86670c40287c71554682963ff320","tid":2386230,"uid":175943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"sofi買唔到sofi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a064699f82b86783968eb8b9b01fff1371c4b08","tid":2386230,"uid":11378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0609ebd54dd8572f34993151ccedc87b7d601de3","tid":2386230,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"長話短說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下影片有介紹Chamath背景<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aNY0sqSXmJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaNY0sqSXmJE&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=ce86cb45\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aNY0sqSXmJE</a><br />\n<br />\nChamath 經此一役聲明大噪<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wgYZk9Mc804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwgYZk9Mc804&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=c043dadc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wgYZk9Mc804</a><br />\n<br />\n以往由大戶主導嘅股票市場，將被散戶主導，美股將會A股化，源於散戶參與程度大大提高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n散戶參與程度提高有以下原因：<br />\n1. 打工過生活唔work，例如要做個識炒股嘅律師，用律師嘅人工去炒股<br />\n2. 智能電話普及，資訊愈來愈流通<br />\n3. 社交群體圍爐<br />\n以上原因集中於一大班不同國家嘅年輕人<img src=\